,"body":"Can I play again?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":334,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":334,"voiceId":"event190-04-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Violin Teacher","body":"Why don't we take a break first? You've already been at it for two hours.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":334}],"windowDisplayName":"Rui","body":"I can still play. Please?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":334,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":334,"voiceId":"event190-04-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Violin Teacher","body":"Hmm~. Playing more might stop it from being fun, you know?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":334}],"windowDisplayName":"Rui","body":"Really...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":334,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":334,"voiceId":"event190-04-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Violin Teacher","body":"No matter how much you love the violin, it becomes hard to have fun when you're tired.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Violin Teacher","body":"That's why it's important to rest properly and come back \"refreshed.\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":334}],"windowDisplayName":"Rui","body":"\"Refreshed?\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":334,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":334,"voiceId":"event190-04-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Violin Teacher","body":"It means getting back your energy so that you can enjoy playing the violin again.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Violin Teacher","body":"I know it's important to practice a lot to get a gold prize, but it'll be really sad if it causes you pain.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Violin Teacher","body":"Not to mention, the best way to play well is to have fun doing it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":334}],"windowDisplayName":"Rui","body":"... I love playing the violin. Does that mean I can get a gold prize?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":334,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":334,"voiceId":"event190-04-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Violin Teacher","body":"Yes, I'm sure you'll be able to.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":334}],"windowDisplayName":"Rui","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSync